task.summary: Default task

fixed wall collision in circleBs don't regenerate the color code every time max velocity is now the current radius removed unused js in overview renamed title in overview added black border to circleBs
fixed image download in clusterFilter changed the way downloadCanvas works (now also works for bigger images) added new preview image for clusterFilter
added archimedean spiral
changed default value for archimedean spiral added todo
only start filling the canvas with the image when the image has finished loading
added collatzConjecture renamed ulamspiral to spiral only calculate the incremental once in the creation of the clusters
increased possible maximum of second value fixed second value using the first valueField
increased maximum spread to 30
the new elements are now calculated while the tree is being drawn changed to use the gradient of colors not the absolut values
minor fixed regarding gradient, still not working correctly with a different number of colors
added js for calculating the 'average' flag of all the flags
fixed local copy of the clusterfilter
added download to flags added flags in overview minor improvements in clusterfilter
added dotLines added dotLines to overview renamed images in overview
refactored some projects to use requestAnimationFrame instead of setTimeout refactored some config layout
added triangles project changed dotLines to be screen size instead of static values
fixed minor bug with color
triangles now disappear if the move to far away from the spawn point instead of mouse pointer
added dependency to msDropdown for drop downs with images added possibility to select color schemes in triangles
Triangles: -removed names from color schemes -use the generic select creation function instead of the customized one Common: -added function to create selects with canvases in them

Triangles: -moved background and colorscheme selector to top left of canvas -canvas now stretches over all the screen -added ability to select a background color Common: -msDropdown with roundedBorders false as default
circleBs: -canvas is now all over the page and controls within the canvas
dotLines: -canvas now covers all the screen common: -created top class for all the controls, not usable with the canvas dropdowns

jsTree: -removed height & width config -removed oil effect - showing noise image will cause it to appear behind the canvas with an opacity of 0.5 -moved a lot of config into the advanced tab -canvas is now the background of the whole page (not really working on mobile...) Triangles: -moved picker to next row for mobile
common: -moved recording stuff to common, maybe used somewhere else added fireWorks! -simple version of fireworks with one rocket type and one color default selected
fireWorks: -added rocket whose flares explode and add some more flares
fireWork: -replaced the slope function with a generalized function to act for flares and rockets -rockets now also work with age
fireWork: -only using one flare function

fireWork: -now using different color schemes -two explosion rockets now spawn with a chance -the color scheme is changed with a chance for the second explosion (not magenta and green) -the color for an element in the trail is changed every frame to an element of the color scheme
Overview: -added fireWorks to overview

fireWorks: -instead of string replace, use concatenation for alpha setting -don't render the trailItem if the alpha is to low -reduced flare amount for primary and secondary flares -the color of the second flare is not decided upon creation of the rocket -refactored the illegalTransition function -instead of the subFlares being stored in the rocket, moved them to their own flare respectively
fireWorks: -rockets now have a chance for the first flare to have bigger heads -removing not rendered elements from lists of trails/flares/rockets -increased falling speed, so it is noticeable
fireWorks: -reduced the factor of the headsize -introduced some central variables
fireWorks: -added actual second explosion which happens after the first one

fireWorks: -added chance for trails to be far longer (secondary and primary) -don't add trails to the list if they are out of the canvas area -restructured config object -added some more values to config object

fireWorks: -fixed objects without eventFun not being able to explode twice (only relevant for flares) -added chance for flares to explode twice, primary has chance reduced because of lag, secondary not working, because secondary has no eventFun
fireWorks: -changed forEach to normal for loops, it seems performance is better
fireWorks: -replaced ctx.drawRect with directly modifying the underlying imageData, great improvement of performance!
fireWorks: -changed controls to be two independent mouse clicks instead of dragging, dragging lagged and did not work on mobile
orbitingSpheres: -added it!
orbitingSpheres: -added hotkey to update whether we show a name or not -updated preview
orbitingSpheres: -fixed preview -fixed hotkey for showing names
